                        <h2>About company</h2>
                    </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="about-content">
                    
                    <p style="font-size: medium">SMS Systems Advisory Group provides services in the field of management consulting and management system organization in Uzbekistan and CIS countries.</p>
                    <p style="font-size: medium">SMS Systems Advisory Group has extensive experience and offers its services since 2006. During this period, the company has been implemented more than 100 projects in leading enterprises of Uzbekistan that have successfully passed certification in various international certification bodies, such as TUV Thuringhen (DGA), Russian Register (RVI), Bureau Veritas, Cert International (SNAS), DQS GmbH (DGA), SGS (UKAS) and others.</p>
                    <p style="font-size: medium">The company has successfully implemented projects for the reengineering and optimization of business processes of organizations.</p>
                    <p style="font-size: medium">Our consultants were trained and worked in leading companies in the country and abroad.</p>
                    <p style="font-size: medium">Our project managers are leading auditors of internationally recognized certification bodies in Germany, Slovakia and Russia.</p>
                </div>
